~ start
Protag: [i] Damn, this guy looks tired. He also looks pretty smart, I should be careful with what strategies I use to interrogate him. [/i] [#sprite=04]
Alan: Hey, are we able to finish this interrogation quickly? I really want to get home and sleep. I’ve been up for the past 16 hours working and I really don’t need to be here.[#sprite=01]
Protag: Sorry, I have to interrogate all of the potential suspects. Why are you in such a rush to get home?[#sprite=01]
Alan: I’m just trying to get home to sleep and prepare for my night shift.[#sprite=02]
Alan: Anyways, are you going to get to asking your questions?[#sprite=01]
Protag: Right. Where were you yesterday?[#sprite=03]
Alan: I arrived at Douglass’s house at one o’clock. I left at around four o’clock to go check on another patient of mine. After that, I went home.[#sprite=03]
Protag: Around what time was that?[#sprite=01]
Alan: Eight o’clock or so.[#sprite=02]
Protag: Did you go anywhere after that?[#sprite=05]
Alan: No. I was at home until the police knocked on my door to take me in for questioning.[#sprite=03]
Protag: Did you see anything suspicious while you were there?[#sprite=04]
Alan: His granddaughter dropped by while I was there, but not much happened. I wouldn’t say it was suspicious or anything.[#sprite=02]
Protag: Anything else to report?[#sprite=01]
Alan: Not really. Got any more questions for me, or am I free to go?[#sprite=01]
Protag: [i] I don’t know if this is something I should ask him, but I can’t help but shake a suspicion I’ve been having. Claw marks, fur, a bite… All the evidence points towards something else being the culprit. Something… inhuman. [/i] [#sprite=04]
Protag: [i] It feels silly to admit to believing in werewolves, but what else could it possibly mean? [/i] [#sprite=04]
Protag: Before we continue with the interrogation, Can I get your medical expertise on something?[#sprite=05]
Alan: What is it?[#sprite=03]
Protag: We found some suspicious evidence at the crime scene. Fur and claw marks everywhere, and the victim died from a bite that looked like a wolf’s, but far too large. Yesterday was a full moon, too.[#sprite=01]
Protag: I suspect it could mean the victim was killed by a werewolf. I know it’s kind of stupid, werewolves don’t exist anymore, but it’s what the evidence seems to suggest. Would you know anything about this?[#sprite=05]
if Global.werewolf == Global.Character.ALAN
	Alan: Ah, You think he was killed by a werewolf. [#sprite=05]
	Alan: Well… I’m not supposed to talk about it, since it could cause a panic, but there’s been a recent outbreak in lycanthropy cases. It’s been making its way across Europe for years now, and has broken containment into the United States, where it spread like wildfire. [#sprite=04]
else
	Alan: Well… I’m not supposed to talk about it, since it could cause a panic, but there’s been a recent outbreak in lycanthropy cases. It’s been making its way across Europe for years now, and has broken containment into the United States, where it spread like wildfire. [#sprite=04]
Protag: I thought lycanthropy was eradicated ages ago. [#sprite=17]
if Global.werewolf == Global.Character.ALAN
	Alan: So did I, but it’s back. We’re not sure why, so we’re trying to keep it under wraps until we know how to contain it. [#sprite=03]
else
	Alan: Everyone thought so as well, but apparently, it’s back. We’re not sure why, so we’re trying to keep it under wraps until we know how to contain it. [#sprite=03]
Protag: I see, thank you for telling me. Your information is very helpful.[#sprite=05]
Protag: [i] I almost wish my theory wasn’t correct. I don’t think there's a protocol for werewolves at large… [/i] [#sprite=04]
Protag: Can you tell me more about them?[#sprite=05]
Alan: Sorry, I’ve already told you too much. It’s supposed to be confidential.[#sprite=04]
Protag: [i] I need to know more about werewolves. How can I get him to tell me? [/i] [#sprite=04]
- Persuasion
	Protag: If you tell me about it, I’ll leave you alone to nap. [#sprite=02]
	if Global.dice_rolls.alan.roll_r1_persuasion >= Global.roll_checks.alan.persuasion:
		=> persuasion_succeed
	else:
		=> persuasion_fail
- Intimidation
	Protag: How do I know you’re not a werewolf? I don’t know anything about them, I have no way of knowing the signs. [#sprite=05]
	if Global.dice_rolls.alan.roll_r1_intimidation >= Global.roll_checks.alan.intimidation:
		=> intimidation_succeed
	else:
		=> intimidation_fail
- Deception
	Protag: I’m interested in stopping the spread of Lycanthropy, too. If we can catch the werewolves, we can stop them from infecting more people. I can’t help anyone if I don’t know what’s going on. [#sprite=00]
	if Global.dice_rolls.alan.roll_r1_deception >= Global.roll_checks.alan.deception:
		=> deception_succeed
	else:
		=> deception_fail

