~ persuasion_succeed
Alan: Fine, I’ll tell you about it.[#sprite=02]
Alan: With Lycanthropy, not only does the person physically transform into a wolf, they also undergo mental changes.[#sprite=04]
Alan: It doesn’t matter what personality the patient has when they transform, everything is completely overridden to turn them into a beast.[#sprite=01]
Protag: Do you have any information on how they got to America in the first place?[#sprite=01]
Alan: We know it originated in Europe. Presumably, an infected person travelled to the US, and that’s how it spread here. That’s all we know, though.[#sprite=03]
Alan: But, we do know that once one person is infected, and they scratch or bite something, the other person gets infected too, and that’s how the disease spreads.[#sprite=01]
Alan: Which is why we’re currently trying to figure out how to stop it.[#sprite=04]
Protag: That’s interesting… anything else?[#sprite=05]
Alan: Nothing. We’re still trying to figure out every little detail about them.[#sprite=01]
Protag: You seem to have a lot of experience with werewolves… Are you sure YOU’RE not a werewolf?[#sprite=01]
if Global.werewolf == Global.Character.ALAN
	Alan: Seriously? That’s stupid reasoning. [#sprite=03]
	Alan: I’m not a werewolf. I’ve just encountered a lot of cases at the hospital over the last few months.[#sprite=04]
else
	Alan: I’m not a werewolf. I’ve just encountered a lot of cases at the hospital over the last few months.[#sprite=04]
Protag: Alright. Thank you for your cooperation, Alan.[#sprite=01]
Alan: No problem.[#sprite=02]
=> end_dialogue

~ persuasion_fail
Alan: Like I said, it’s classified. That means I can’t talk about it. [#sprite=01]
Protag: I need you to cooperate so I can solve this case. Can you please tell me more? [#sprite=09]
Alan: This is an important international secret. I can’t just leak it to some hotshot detective. [#sprite=02]
Protag: [i] You kind of already did, though… [/i] [#sprite=08]
Protag: Are you sure you can’t tell me anything? [#sprite=01]
Alan: Sorry, no can do. [#sprite=00]
Protag: [i] Dang it, I think that’s the most I’m gonna get. At least I was able to confirm the existence of werewolves, though. [/i] [#sprite=00]
